#: src/admin/components/SetupWizard/index.js
msgid "BimBeau Privacy Analytics can contact referrer domains to retrieve their icons and cache validated copies inside your WordPress installation."
msgstr "BimBeau Privacy Analytics, simgelerini almak ve doğrulanmış kopyaları WordPress kurulumunuz içinde önbelleğe almak için yönlendiren alan adlarıyla iletişime geçebilir."

#: src/admin/components/SetupWizard/index.js
msgid "The contacted domains can receive your server IP address and a generic technical User-Agent. No request is sent directly from the administrator's browser, and no WordPress site URL is included in the User-Agent."
